{"type":"question","id":30319,"title":"如何评价新通过的中国「人民警察」警旗？","uid":3685,"topics":[455,9059,2248,2030,254],"contents":"经党中央批准，警察警旗式样确定。警旗旗面以红蓝两色为主，警徽居于左上角。<br>\n<br>\n据了解，红色体现党对警察的全面领导、绝对领导，彰显了中国警察对党绝对忠诚、绝对纯洁、绝对可靠的政治本色；蓝色代表着人民，凸显了中国警察维持社会和谐稳定的职业特征。&nbsp;<br>\n<br>\nhttps://t.co/GyhWdtv1Pt<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgV4zTIWAAEHYG8?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgV4zTIWAAEHYG8?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgV4zTIWAAEHYG8?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-08-28","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":5}